README
======

Overview
--------

This project is a prototype/demo Django web application for generic
management of items (including ingest, metadata editing, etc.)  in a
Fedora repository.


Components
----------

todo
~~~~
Describe components here as we add them...

System Dependencies
-------------------

findingaids requires the following network resources:

  * LDAP for user authentication
  * A relational database for user and session information
  * Persistent ID manager for minting ARKs to use as Fedora object pids

-----

For more detailed information, including installation instructions and upgrade
notes, see :ref:`DEPLOYNOTES`.  For details about the features included in each release,
see :ref:`CHANGELOG`.


